                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         I am proud to announce that we are the winners of the 2019 New York Tech Valley Judges award. We were bestowed with this honor by the judges after hearing about our team management, extensive bias free tryout process, design process, camaraderie, and analyzing our robot. I would like to extend a huge thanks to Judge Robert Brennan and our Sponsors for believing in our team and for realizing our potential.<br><br><br>
